{"tid":1369686,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 狗員佐級協會要求成立獨立調查委員會","createTime":"2019-07-26T18:19:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T04:11:14.000Z","uid":1251,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"86222383d8b2cb64bfb09d920906e11b8b496cd8","tid":1369686,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:19:53.000Z","msg":"即係叫張建宗要調查清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【員佐級協會：譴責張建宗妄自斷定警隊對錯】<br />\n<br />\n警察隊員佐級協會發表聲明，認為政務司司長張建宗的道歉言論不負責任，抹煞警務人員在這件政治事件上的努力、付出、委屈及犧牲；<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">又指張建宗在未作出調查前</span></span>，及完全不了解警隊運作的情況下，向公眾妄自斷定警隊對錯，協會給予最嚴厲的譴責。<br />\n<br />\n聲明又反問，「作為政務司司長管理香港致如斯境地，我們是否要代表張司長公開道歉敬請明示」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ntqeYAZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FntqeYAZ.png&h=c34ad254&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"15c748d35716fdf8a14cd72ee346a96e90bfe430","tid":1369686,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:20:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c48754756a77a4353e7341538f870438a6cd26c","tid":1369686,"uid":100406,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:22:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5bb984c1edfcf8a3d78caed6bacb574a1e6b84e","tid":1369686,"uid":128569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:33:51.000Z","msg":"彈出彈入"},{"pid":"30a3303c2da3facf3659d73180f872be68d83fdf","tid":1369686,"uid":86194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:36:44.000Z","msg":"全盛時期嘅員佐級協會一日要出幾多封信"},{"pid":"a85b3c30926596f71d29fe039101b26ec5440bce","tid":1369686,"u